                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>The form is filled out in manuscript, possibly in the hand of George Crabbe. Signed by George Crabbe and W. E. Waldron. On the verso is a note in the hand of Crabbe suspending the order on account of the illness of William Merchant, signed by Waldron and Crabbe. Endorsed: Suspending Order for Wm. Merchant.</p>
